==Useful Info==
'''Bone dragons''' are [[undead]] [[list of dragons|draconic]] horrors. They lack a [[breath weapon]], but make up for it with powerful melee capabilities, excellent defense, and plentiful [[HP]]. You can find them in [[the Crypt]], [[the Vaults]], [[the Abyss]], and the [[Hell]]s (primarily [[Tartarus]]), as well as one rune vault in [[the Swamp]].

==Tips & Tricks==
*Bone Dragons are vulnerable to [[Dispel Undead]] and  [[Lee's Rapid Deconstruction]], while powerful non-elemental [[Conjurations]] are also effective. However, it'll still take several shots to kill them.

==History==
*Prior to [[0.12]], bone dragons were slower but had significantly more HP.
